window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ancient evils lurk in the Western New York town of Oneka Falls, and they are hungry.</p> <p>Only three children have encountered them and lived. Psyches fractured, each child has survived as best they could - wrapped in fantasy, the comfort of amnesia, or the silence of isolation.</p> <p>When those evils intrude on their lives a second time, it sets a chain of events in action that can only end in destruction. But who will be destroyed, the children or the ancient evils that plague the town?</p>"; 
